metadata.name: VibeNauts Machina Collectors Card #1/514
metadata.description:
VibeNauts "Machina" was the name given to the Original Members of the VibeNauts Community When we started in January 2022

This NFT Collectors Card has been Created in Commemoration of it being 1 Year since VibeNauts inception and to Honor the Original 500 Collectors of the VibeNauts NFT Project! 

This Artwork will also be used in the Future as the backs of the Phsyical VibeNauts Trading Cards!

Minted and Forever Marked in History
